        "text_qa3Dnt": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Your preferred sleeping position significantly influences which mattress will be the most comfortable for you. Here’s a breakdown:</p><h4><strong>Side Sleepers</strong></h4><p>Side sleepers typically benefit from softer mattresses that provide pressure relief for the shoulders and hips. Consider memory foam or hybrid options.</p><h4><strong>Back Sleepers</strong></h4><p>Back sleepers need medium to firm mattresses to support spinal alignment. Hybrid and innerspring mattresses often work well.</p><h4><strong>Stomach Sleepers</strong></h4><p>Firm mattresses prevent the lower back from sinking, making them ideal for stomach sleepers. Latex and firmer hybrids are great choices.</p><h4><strong>Combination Sleepers</strong></h4><p>If you switch positions throughout the night, opt for a medium-firm mattress with responsive materials like latex or hybrid designs.</p><p><strong>Real-Life Example:</strong><br/>Mark, a marathon runner, used to wake up with tight hips. He switched from a firm spring mattress to a medium-firm hybrid and noticed less stiffness. The extra cushioning helped align his spine without feeling too soft.</p><p>Not sure which firmness is right for you? Read our blog on <a href=\"https://mattressville.ca/blogs/tips/choosing-the-right-firmness\">how to choose mattress firmness</a>.</p><p><br/></p><h3><strong>Step 3: Consider Mattress Sizes</strong></h3><p>Choosing the right size is essential for comfort and practicality. Here’s a quick guide:</p><ul><li><strong>Twin</strong>: Ideal for children or smaller spaces.</li><li><strong>Full</strong>: Great for single adults or guest rooms.</li><li><strong>Queen</strong>: Perfect for couples or those who like extra room.</li><li><strong>King/California King</strong>: Best for families or those who prioritize luxury and space.</li></ul><p>Explore our <a href=\"https://mattressville.ca/pages/mattress-size-guide\">mattress size guide</a> for detailed dimensions.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
